column2: SELECT   n.objID, n.distance, n.type,   p.ra AS pra, p.dec AS pdec, p.modelmag_r,   s.bestobjid FROM Galaxy AS G    OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#, #) AS n    LEFT JOIN PhotoObj AS p ON n.objid=p.objid   LEFT JOIN SpecObj as s ON n.objid=s.bestobjid   WHERE G.objID = n.objID INTO MyDB.NearbyObjEq
